---
<section class="bg-[#fdfaf5] py-16 px-4">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto flex flex-col gap-12">
    <div class="text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif font-bold text-[#5e4b42] mb-4">Nous Trouver</h2>
      <div class="w-16 h-1 bg-teal-500 mx-auto"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8">
      <div class="flex-1">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md mb-4">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-serif font-bold text-teal-500 mb-4">Notre Adresse</h3>
          <div class="flex flex-col space-y-2">
            <span class="flex items-center space-x-3 text-[#5e4b42]">
              <img src="/icons/map-pin.svg" alt="Adresse" class="w-5 h-5" />
              <span>10 Avenue Général Charles De Gaulle, 71880 Châtenoy-le-Royal</span>
            </span>
            <span class="flex items-center space-x-3 text-[#5e4b42]">
              <img src="/icons/clock.svg" alt="Horaires" class="w-5 h-5" />
              <span>Lundi et Mercredi - Dimanche: 6h30 - 13h, 16h - 19h</span>
            </span>
            <span class="flex items-center space-x-3 text-[#5e4b42]">
              <img src="/icons/phone.svg" alt="Téléphone" class="w-5 h-5" />
              <span>03 85 XX XX XX</span>
            </span>
            <span class="flex items-center space-x-3 text-[#5e4b42]">
              <img src="/icons/email.svg" alt="Email" class="w-5 h-5" />
              <span>contact@jouvenceaux-boulangerie.fr</span>
            </span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-[#5e4b42] leading-relaxed">
          Facilement accessible, notre boulangerie est au cœur du village. Profitez d'un parking à proximité et 
          offrez-vous une pause gourmande lors de vos promenades.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex-1 rounded-lg shadow-md overflow-hidden">
        <!-- Replace the '...' with your actual Google Maps embed link -->
        <iframe src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d2886.XXXXXXX!2d4.XXXXXXX!3d46.XXXXXXX!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0xXXXXXXX%3A0xXXXXXXX!2sBoulangerie%20Jouvenceaux!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sfr!4vYYYYYYYYYYYYY" allowfullscreen="" loading="lazy" referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade" class="w-full h-64 md:h-full"></iframe>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
